d savings reached US$1988.5 billion and 1411.8 billion, respectively. Potential ACE reached 36.3 \u00b1 5.4 Tg. CONCLUSIONS Our study provides evidence for the potential benefits of biological controllers on economic losses and carbon emissions, which can be incorporated into sustainable development in low-income countries.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Alaniz, Alberto J", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "N\u00fa\u00f1ez-Hidalgo, Ignacio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Carvajal, Mario A", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alvarenga, Thiago M", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "G\u00f3mez-Cantillana, Paulina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vergara, Pablo M", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 5", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1a90803eed2862f29f2f3bd233713efd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3f19dc2e341432d80c1a8b8c6fd5dc6d9ec4b8560e6596f2fc5330c3d79aa293", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/QSA2HIMY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/QSA2HIMY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/6ef5dc641f104adaa806ba6e93db2042!/b174496-176607", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1002/ps.5776", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article",